text: Well this was a very very fun time a lot of things are doing for most of the Resident  evil 8 stuff and the 4 remake stuff it actually looks pretty good.  I was getting a bit terrified when I heard that they were gonna do things in a bit more of a serious tone to match with the recent remakes but thankfully Leon still has some one liners and the merchant is available meaning there's still a good amount of that Resident Evil four cheesy soul for the most part.  Plus it definitely does look like that capcom is trying to stick to the roots of the main game but not go overboard with it. Here's hoping that when it does come out we'll have all the features from the original game back in some way shape or form preferably in the base game and not through DLC. As for the other capcom stuff that we watched before the I've watched before the showcase started seeing Gura freaking out about all the other capcom related projects is just adorable lol.  And now the image of her eating chicken nuggets while watching video game footage is just way too cute.  But again this was a nice surprise to watch this with you gura and a very fun and entertaining stream as always and here's hoping that you'll be able to get permission to play the RE4 remake when it comes out!
